@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam backgroundColor white

title The Global Services Monitor

package "Local Services (PRIMARY_INDEX node)" {
    component "Process Manager" as PM
    component "Internal Queue" as IQ
    component "GSMonitor\n(AsyncIO task)" as GSM
}

component "Global Services\n(managed process)" as GS

PM --> IQ : SHFwdOutput\nor SHProcessExit\n(from GS stdout/stderr\nor GS process exit)
IQ --> GSM : dequeue message
GSM --> GS : monitor lifecycle

GS --> PM : stdout: serialized GSHalted\nor other output

note right of GSM
  GSMonitor runs as an AsyncIO task.
  It sits quietly waiting for input
  on the internal queue.
  Handles GSHalted to coordinate
  controlled shutdown.
end note

note bottom of IQ
  This internal queue is NOT
  a Dragon Channel — it is an
  in-process structure used only
  for GS monitoring.
end note

@enduml
